---
title: Cheesy Saucy Mexican Chickpea Enchiladas with Charred Corn Salsa & Sour Cream
description: With chickpeas, tortillas, Cheddar cheese and charred sweetcorn salsa, this Mexican favourite is colourful, delicious and a heap of fun to make. Don’t forget to dollop on the sour cream to really get the fiesta going!

